verbs.description: President Donald Trump [V: has] promoted his " America First " agenda during an appearance in Cleveland . Trump spent several hours in Ohio on Saturday meeting with supporters and participating in a roundtable designed to highlight the benefits of the new Republican tax law . Striking a celebratory tone , Trump listed his poll numbers and recounted the successes of his first year in office . He also looked ahead to his meeting with North Korea 's Kim Jong Un .
